"that folder. Books in the folder are nicely arranged into sub-folders by "
"Author and Title. Note that the contents of this folder are automatically "
"managed by |app|, **do not** add any files/folders manually to this folder, "
"as they may be automatically deleted. If you want to add a file associated "
"to a particular book, use the top right area of :guilabel:`Edit metadata` "
"dialog to do so. Then, |app| will automatically put that file into the "
"correct folder and move it around when the title/author changes."
